# ITMANO CRM — Cursor Rules

## Project summary
Multi-tenant SaaS CRM for real estate lead management built with Next.js 14 App Router.
Currently in Phase 1 (UI mockup with static data). No backend yet.

## Stack
Next.js 14 App Router · TypeScript strict · shadcn/ui · Tailwind CSS · framer-motion · recharts · lucide-react

## Critical rules

### Colors
- CRM pages: ALWAYS use CSS variables (`var(--accent-gold)`, `var(--text-primary)`, etc.)
- Funnel pages: ALWAYS use the `C` constant object — never CSS variables
- Never hardcode hex colors in CRM components

### Components
- Default to Server Components. Add `'use client'` only when needed (state, effects, framer-motion, recharts)
- Never import recharts in Server Components
- Never use AOS library (breaks Next.js SSR)

### Data
- Phase 1: ALL data from `lib/mockdata.ts` — no fetch(), no API calls, no Supabase
- Import directly: `import { MOCK_LEADS, MOCK_AGENTS } from '@/lib/mockdata'`
- TypeScript strict: never use `any`

### Route groups
- `(dashboard)` → CRM with sidebar + topbar, dark theme, CSS variables
- `(funnel)` → Public marketing pages, light warm theme, C object
- `(auth)` → Login page, dark theme

### File structure
```
app/(dashboard)/leads/page.tsx         → Leads table + kanban
app/(dashboard)/leads/new/page.tsx     → Manual lead form + CSV import
app/(dashboard)/leads/[id]/page.tsx    → Lead detail
app/(dashboard)/dashboard/page.tsx     → Main dashboard
app/(dashboard)/analytics/page.tsx     → Server Component, passes data to chart clients
app/(funnel)/lm/guia-familias-hispanas/page.tsx → Lead magnet funnel
lib/mockdata.ts                         → All static data
lib/types.ts                            → Domain types
```

### Agents and their colors
```
agent-adriana → #5B8EC9 blue   (Hispanic families, ES)
agent-john    → #5AAFA0 teal   (Military, EN)
agent-melanie → #C97B6B coral  (First buyers, ES/EN)
agent-viviane → #B87BA3 pink   (Brazilian, PT)
```

### Lead status flow
new → nurturing → warm → hot → process_started → process_completed → closed | lost

### DO NOT
- Add Supabase or any DB connection (Phase 2)
- Import framer-motion in Server Components
- Use hardcoded colors in CRM
- Use CSS variables in funnel pages
- Use AOS library